<br><br>
Let's play Football.<br><br>
Now, I know why I enjoyed six men football in the corps so much. <br>
We trained and practice after our duty assignments, then played against Army, Navy and Air Force when football was their assignment. <br>
We never won a game, but gosh, I loved those days. It made no difference who won, afterwards, we all always ended up at the nearest watering hole. I don't believe we ever talked about Nam, guess it wasn't appropriate to do so.<br>

